mengenai pengaturan tempat duduk.

744
00:52:38.905 --> 00:52:40.365
Saya harap Anda bekerja sama.

745
00:52:40.448 --> 00:52:41.783
Ya, tuan.

746
00:52:43.326 --> 00:52:45.453
